flowchart TD
    A[Prompt from frontend] --> B[Load Session / Memory State]

    B --> C{Interpret in Context}

    C -->|Question / explanation| D[BioinformaticsGuru]
    D --> E[Persist conversation state]
    E --> F[Respond to user]

    C -->|New workflow request| G[Resolve artifacts / historical state]
    C -->|Follow-up on prior artifacts| G
    C -->|Debug failed run| G
    C -->|Answer to clarification| H[Resume from saved checkpoint]
    C -->|Provide missing inputs| I[Bind inputs to pending workflow]
    C -->|Approve pending plan| J[Execute approved plan]
    C -->|Revise / reject plan| K[Workflow Planner Agent]

    H --> G
    I --> G

    G --> L{Artifacts / state resolved?}

    L -->|Ambiguous| M[Ask for clarification]
    L -->|Missing inputs / missing artifact| N[Ask for required inputs]
    L -->|Resolved| K

    K --> O{Enough context to plan?}

    O -->|No| M
    O -->|Yes| P[Build / revise workflow plan]

    P --> Q{Concrete inputs available for execution?}

    Q -->|No| N
    Q -->|Yes| R{User approval required?}

    R -->|Yes| S[Present plan to user]
    S --> T[Save checkpoint: WAITING_FOR_APPROVAL]
    T --> F

    R -->|No| U[Infrastructure Decision Agent]

    C -->|Approve pending plan| V[Load pending plan + checkpoint]
    V --> W{Bindings valid?}
    W -->|No| N
    W -->|Yes| U

    M --> X[Save checkpoint: WAITING_FOR_CLARIFICATION]
    X --> F

    N --> Y[Save checkpoint: WAITING_FOR_INPUTS]
    Y --> F

    U --> Z{All tools available?}

    Z -->|Yes| AA[Execute Pipeline]
    Z -->|No| AB{Can compose or generate?}

    AB -->|Compose existing tools| AA
    AB -->|Generate new tool| AC[Tool Generator Agent]
    AC --> AA
    AB -->|Cannot proceed safely| M

    AA --> AD{Successful execution?}

    AD -->|Yes| AE[Register artifacts]
    AE --> AF[Update lineage + branch state]
    AF --> AG[Save state: COMPLETED]
    AG --> AH[Report results to user]
    AH --> F

    AD -->|Needs user input| AI[Ask for additional inputs / clarification]
    AI --> AJ[Save checkpoint: FAILED_WAITING_FOR_USER]
    AJ --> F

    AD -->|No| AK[Failure Recovery / Bug Fix Agent]

    AK --> AL{Recovery path}

    AL -->|Retry step| AA
    AL -->|Patch and rerun| AA
    AL -->|Need user guidance| AJ

    subgraph Memory_and_State
        B1[Conversation memory]
        B2[Workflow state]
        B3[Artifact registry]
        B4[Lineage / branches]
        B5[Checkpoint manager]
    end

    B --- B1
    B --- B2
    G --- B3
    AF --- B4
    X --- B5
    Y --- B5
    T --- B5
    AJ --- B5